The paper discusses a new paradigm for implementing inference in belief networks, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely categories. The paper also discusses the reduction of software and hardware resources required for utilizing belief networks in real-world applications, which is related to data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper mentions the development of on-line inference on different software and hardware platforms, which is related to databases (cs.DB).
